==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Appropriator
<hw>Ap*pro"pri*a`tor</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who appropriates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A spiritual corporation possessed
of an appropriated benefice; also, an impropriator.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Approvable</ent>⟦br⟧
